          "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n</head>\n<body style=\"font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px;\">\n<div style=\"max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px;\">\n<h2 style=\"color: #374151; margin: 0 0 20px 0;\">Unsubscribed Successfully</h2>\n<p style=\"color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;\">Hi {{first_name}},</p>\n<p style=\"color: #4b5563; font-size: 16px;\">You have been successfully removed from <strong>{{list_name}}</strong>.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;\">You will no longer receive emails from this list.</p>\n<p style=\"color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 24px;\">\nChanged your mind? <a href=\"{{resubscribe_url}}\" style=\"color: #f59e0b;\">Resubscribe here</a>.\n</p>\n<hr style=\"border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 24px 0;\">\n<p style=\"color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;\">🐝 Bee.AI | <a href=\"{{preferences_url}}\" style=\"color: #9ca3af;\">Email Preferences</a></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>",
          "body_text": "Unsubscribed Successfully\n\nHi {{first_name}},\n\nYou have been successfully removed from {{list_name}}.\nYou will no longer receive emails from this list.\n\nChanged your mind? Resubscribe here: {{resubscribe_url}}\n\n🐝 Bee.AI\nEmail Preferences: {{preferences_url}}"
        }
